        </p>
      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec72-2">
        <p>
          Let <m>R = \left\{ { {\left( {x, y} \right) \in \mathbb{R} \times \mathbb{R} } \mid \left| x \right| + \left| y \right| = 4} \right\}</m>.
          Then <m>R</m> is a relation on <m>\mathbb{R}</m>.
